GENE_ID: 0x464942
DESC: Fibonacci sequence protein — computes Fib(N) via DNAsm VM
TYPE: algorithmic
ALGORITHM: dnasm_fibonacci_v8
INPUT: N (non-negative integer)
OUTPUT: Fib(N)
ATP_COST: 50
REFERENCE: simulator/dnasm_exec.c
PROGRAM:
LOAD r0
NUM 0
STORE r3 r1
NUM 1
STORE r3 r2
NUM 1
STORE r3 r4
LABEL loop
CMP r4 r0
JGT end
FIB r1 r2
STORE r2 r1
INC r4
JMP loop
LABEL end
PRINT r1
HALT
